This product is an open-source client intake, eligibility, case- and
service-management, and CSBG Annual Report system for Community Action
Agencies. It is built around the data requirements of the CSBG Annual
Report 3.0 (OMB No. 0970-0492) and the HHS Federal Poverty Guidelines.

CAP Trellis is not endorsed by or affiliated with the U.S. Department of
Health and Human Services, the Administration for Children and Families,
the Office of Community Services, NASCSP, or the National Community
Action Partnership. CSBG taxonomy labels reproduced in this software are
drawn from public federal reporting instruments.

Bundled fonts and brand assets under public/brand and src/fonts may be
subject to their own licenses; deployments replace these with their own
organization's assets via Settings.
